        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[CFTC 主席 Rostin Behnam：沒有監督的 DeFi 像無照醫生]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>商品期貨交易委員會 (CFTC) 主席 Rostin Behnam 在週一的演講中強調了監督去中心化金融 (DeFi) 的必要性，並稱沒有監督的 DeFi 像「無照醫生」，主<span class="s2">管機關應超前佈署，不能等</span>到受害者遭受痛苦並大聲尋求幫助時才採取行動。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/cftc-chairman-rostin-behnam-defi-need-to-be-overseen#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-651b788adc4d0"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-651b788adc4d0"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/cftc-chairman-rostin-behnam-defi-need-to-be-overseen/#CFTC_%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%B0_DeFi_%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0" title="CFTC 連續開罰 DeFi 協議">CFTC 連續開罰 DeFi 協議</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/cftc-chairman-rostin-behnam-defi-need-to-be-overseen/#%E9%80%99%E4%BA%9B_DeFi_%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E5%83%8F%E7%84%A1%E7%85%A7%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F" title="這些 DeFi 協議像無照醫生">這些 DeFi 協議像無照醫生</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/cftc-chairman-rostin-behnam-defi-need-to-be-overseen/#Brian_Armstrong_%E7%A8%B1%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%96%BC_DeFi" title="Brian Armstrong 稱商品交易法不應適用於 DeFi">Brian Armstrong 稱商品交易法不應適用於 DeFi</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="CFTC_%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%B0_DeFi_%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0"></span>CFTC 連續開罰 DeFi 協議<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>CFTC 在九月初與 DeFi 協議 Opyn、ZeroEx 和 Deridex 達成和解，這些協議分別需支付 25 萬美元、20 萬美元和 10 萬美元的民事罰款。</p><p>Deridex 和 Opyn 被指控未能註冊為換匯 (swap) 執行機構或指定合約市場、未能註冊為期貨佣金商，以及未能採用客戶身分識別計畫作為銀行保密法合規計畫的一部分。而 ZeroEx、Opyn 和 Deridex 也被監管機構指控非法提供數位資產槓桿和保證金零售商品交易。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E9%80%99%E4%BA%9B_DeFi_%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E5%83%8F%E7%84%A1%E7%85%A7%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F"></span><span class="s2">這些 </span>DeFi 協議像無照醫生<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p><span class="s1">根據 <a href="https://www.theblock.co/post/254024/cftc-chair-rostin-behnam-turns-his-focus-to-getting-ahead-of-defi?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Block 的報導</a>，Behnam 在</span><span class="s2">芝加哥期貨產業協會博覽會上發表了談話，稱主管機關不能等</span>到受害者遭受痛苦並大聲尋求幫助時才採取主動行動。確保關鍵的市場監督、強大的網路安全和系統保障以及客戶保護，是 CFTC 的使命和宗旨。</p><p class="content">想一想，如果只要求某些人擁有駕駛執照，你在路上是否會感到安心？或者，如果有選擇的話，你是否會將你的醫療保健委託給未經培訓或無執照的醫生。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Brian_Armstrong_%E7%A8%B1%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%96%BC_DeFi"></span>Brian Armstrong 稱商品交易法不應適用於 DeFi<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Coinbase 執行長 Brian Armstrong 之前也就此事發表了看法，他希望這些 DeFi 協議能告上法庭，並樹立先例。</p><p class="content">CFTC 不應該對 DeFi 協議採取執法行動。他們不是金融服務企業，《商品交易法》不太可能適用於它們。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">The CFTC should not be creating enforcement actions against decentralized (DeFi) protocols. These are not financial service businesses, and it’s highly unlikely the Commodity Exchange Act even applies to them.</p><p>My hope is these DeFi protocols take these cases to court to…</p><p>— Brian Armstrong 🛡️ (@brian_armstrong) <a href="https://twitter.com/brian_armstrong/status/1702043655928955139?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 13, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p>
]]>
            </description>
